    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288600/extras/b964deec53b8f3acde2cd00df6d04146.poster.avif?t=1758563303\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288600/extras/b964deec53b8f3acde2cd00df6d04146.webm?t=1758563303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288600/extras/b964deec53b8f3acde2cd00df6d04146.mp4?t=1758563303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Skibidi Gyatrooms 是一款 1-4 人的合作恐怖探索游戏。你和朋友们刚刚掉进了后室，但这可不是普通的走廊。唯一比被困在过渡空间更可怕的，就是 Skibidi 厕所带着满满的魅力和零冷静向你袭来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288600/extras/e9595d144b496df24ab962441824977a.poster.avif?t=1758563303\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288600/extras/e9595d144b496df24ab962441824977a.webm?t=1758563303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288600/extras/e9595d144b496df24ab962441824977a.mp4?t=1758563303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你得在这瓷器西格玛威胁前秀出自己的 GYAT，否则就会毫不留情地被冲走。觉得自己有能力单独逃脱？可以，但别忘了带上队伍。我们在说疯狂更新、诅咒关卡，以及足够让你脑袋转个不停的烧脑体验。你能生存下 GYAT 的考验还是会被冲走？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288600/extras/53b73ee189855e892afc28d4a8a411db.poster.avif?t=1758563303\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288600/extras/53b73ee189855e892afc28d4a8a411db.webm?t=1758563303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288600/extras/53b73ee189855e892afc28d4a8a411db.mp4?t=1758563303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
